query.sfwSql: SELECT DISTINCT SDN.*, SP.MPI_PERSON_ID as MPI_PERSON_ID ,SP.FIRST_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME, SP.SSN,SP.DATE_OF_BIRTH ,istrRelativeVipFlag = ( SELECT CASE WHEN (COUNT(*) > 0 OR SP.VIP_FLAG='Y') THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END FROM SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SPP ON SPP.PERSON_ID = SR.PERSON_ID WHERE (SR.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = SP.PERSON_ID OR SR.DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID = SP.PERSON_ID) AND SPP.VIP_FLAG = 'Y') FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION SDN WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP WITH(NOLOCK) on SP.PERSON_ID = SDN.PERSON_ID

SELECT SPL.PLAN_NAME istrPlan,SPAB.*,SP.PERSON_ID,SR.*,SPL.PLAN_ID iaintPlan FROM SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR WITH(NOLOCK) JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY SPAB WITH(NOLOCK) ON SR.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID=SPAB.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA WITH(NOLOCK) ON SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID=SPAB.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID JOIN SGT_PLAN SPL WITH(NOLOCK) ON SPA.PLAN_ID=SPL.PLAN_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SPA.PERSON_ID=SP.PERSON_ID WHERE SR.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID=@person_id AND SP.PERSON_ID > 0 and (spab.END_DATE is null or spab.END_DATE =(select DATE_OF_DEATH from SGT_PERSON where PERSON_ID = @person_id))

SELECT SR.*,SP.PERSON_ID FROM SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR WITH(NOLOCK) LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SR.PERSON_ID=SP.PERSON_ID WHERE SR.DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID=@person_id and (SR.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE is null or SR.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE=SP.DATE_OF_DEATH)
SELECT * FROM SGT_DRO_APPLICATION WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID
SELECT * FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE (BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE='RTMT' OR BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE='DSBL' OR BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE='WDRL') AND PERSON_ID=@person_id
SELECT COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'CRTF'
select top(2)* from SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_STATUS_HISTORY WITH(NOLOCK) where BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID=@BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID order by STATUS_DATE DESC
select top(2)* from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION_STATUS_HISTORY WITH(NOLOCK) where DRO_APPLICATION_ID=@DRO_APPLICATION_ID order by STATUS_DATE DESC

select spb.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID, sp.PERSON_ID iaintBenID,sp.FIRST_NAME + ' ' + sp.LAST_NAME istrBenFullName, spl.PLAN_NAME istrPlan,spb.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE ,spab.*,sp.MPI_PERSON_ID as istrBenMPID,spl.PLAN_ID iaintPlan from SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY spab WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT spa WITH(NOLOCK) on spa.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = spab.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID join SGT_PLAN spl WITH(NOLOCK) on spa.PLAN_ID = spl.PLAN_ID right outer join SGT_RELATIONSHIP spb WITH(NOLOCK) on spab.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID = spb.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID join SGT_PERSON sp WITH(NOLOCK) on sp.PERSON_ID = spb.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID JOIN SGT_PERSON SP1 ON SP1.PERSON_ID=SPB.PERSON_ID where spb.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and spb.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID is NOT NULL and (spab.END_DATE is null or spab.END_DATE=SP1.DATE_OF_DEATH) union select spb.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID, spb.BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID ,so.ORG_NAME istrBenFullName, spl.PLAN_NAME istrPlan,spb.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE ,spab.*,so.MPI_ORG_ID as istrBenMPID,spl.PLAN_ID iaintPlan from SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY spab join SGT_RELATIONSHIP spb on spab.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID = spb.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID join SGT_ORGANIZATION so on so.ORG_ID = spb.BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID join SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT spa WITH(NOLOCK) on spa.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = spab.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID join SGT_PLAN spl WITH(NOLOCK) on spa.PLAN_ID = spl.PLAN_ID JOIN SGT_PERSON SP1 ON SP1.PERSON_ID=SPB.PERSON_ID where spb.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and spb.BENEFICIARY_ORG_ID is NOT NULL and (spab.END_DATE is null OR spab.END_DATE=SP1.DATE_OF_DEATH) order by PLAN_NAME, BENEFICIARY_TYPE_VALUE

SELECT (SP.FIRST_NAME + ' ' + SP.LAST_NAME)as 'istrFullName',SPD.* FROM SGT_RELATIONSHIP SPD WITH(NOLOCK) JOIN SGT_PERSON SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SP.PERSON_ID=SPD.DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID JOIN SGT_PERSON SP1 ON SP1.PERSON_ID=SPD.PERSON_ID WHERE SPD.PERSON_ID=@person_id and SPD.DEPENDENT_PERSON_ID is NOT NULL and (SPD.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE is null or SPD.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE=SP1.DATE_OF_DEATH)

SELECT DISTINCT SDN.*, 'R' AS STATUS, SP.MPI_PERSON_ID istrMpiPersonId ,SP.LAST_NAME+ ', ' +SP.FIRST_NAME istrName, SP.SSN ,SP.DATE_OF_BIRTH idtDateOfBirth ,APP_STATUS = '',UNION_CODE = '' ,UNION_CODE_DESC = '', SP.FIRST_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME,'XXX-XX-' + SUBSTRING(SP.SSN,6,4) AS SS4, ABS(DATEDIFF(DAY,SP.DATE_OF_BIRTH,ISNULL(SP.DATE_OF_DEATH,GETDATE()))/365) AS AGE FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION SDN WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SP.PERSON_ID = SDN.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH(NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ID = SP.PERSON_ID WHERE DATEPART(MM,SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE) = DATEPART(MM, DATEADD(MM,-1,GETDATE())) AND DATEPART(YEAR,SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE) = DATEPART(YEAR, DATEADD(MM,-1,GETDATE())) --AND DATEPART(MM,SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE) <> DATEPART(MM, ISNULL(SDN.NOTIFICATION_CHANGE_DATE,'99991231')) --AND DATEPART(YEAR,SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE) = DATEPART(YEAR, DATEADD(MM,-1,ISNULL(SDN.NOTIFICATION_CHANGE_DATE,'99991231'))) AND PA.BENEFECIARY_OF_PERSON_ID IS NULL AND PA.BENEFECIARY_PERSON_ID IS NULL AND SP.PERSON_ID IN (SELECT ISNULL(SPA1.PERSON_ID,0) FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA1 LEFT JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ) AND SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_ID = (SELECT TOP(1) DEATH_NOTIFICATION_ID FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION D1 WHERE SDN.PERSON_ID = D1.PERSON_ID ORDER BY CREATED_DATE DESC)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT SDN.*, 'A' AS STATUS, SP.MPI_PERSON_ID istrMpiPersonId ,SP.LAST_NAME + ', ' +SP.FIRST_NAME istrName, SP.SSN ,SP.DATE_OF_BIRTH idtDateOfBirth ,APP_STATUS = '',UNION_CODE = '' ,UNION_CODE_DESC = '', SP.FIRST_NAME, SP.LAST_NAME,'XXX-XX-' + SUBSTRING(SP.SSN,6,4) AS SS4, ABS(DATEDIFF(DAY,SP.DATE_OF_BIRTH,ISNULL(SP.DATE_OF_DEATH,GETDATE()))/365) AS AGE FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION SDN WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP WITH(NOLOCK) ON SP.PERSON_ID = SDN.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH(NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ID = SP.PERSON_ID WHERE DATEPART(MM,SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE) = DATEPART(MM, DATEADD(MM,-1,GETDATE())) AND DATEPART(YEAR,SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE) = DATEPART(YEAR, DATEADD(MM,-1,GETDATE())) --AND DATEPART(MM,SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE) <> DATEPART(MM, ISNULL(SDN.NOTIFICATION_CHANGE_DATE,'99991231')) --AND DATEPART(YEAR,SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE) = DATEPART(YEAR, DATEADD(MM,-1,ISNULL(SDN.NOTIFICATION_CHANGE_DATE,'99991231'))) AND PA.BENEFECIARY_OF_PERSON_ID IS NULL AND PA.BENEFECIARY_PERSON_ID IS NULL AND SP.PERSON_ID NOT IN (SELECT ISNULL(SPA1.PERSON_ID,0) FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA1 LEFT JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ) AND SDN.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_ID = (SELECT TOP(1) DEATH_NOTIFICATION_ID FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION D1 WHERE SDN.PERSON_ID = D1.PERSON_ID ORDER BY CREATED_DATE DESC)
SELECT COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'DSBL' OR BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RTMT') AND APPLICATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'APPR'
SELECT * FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE='DDPR' AND PERSON_ID=@person_id
select DATE_OF_DEATH from SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION where DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'CRTF' and PERSON_ID =@PERSON_ID

SELECT COUNT(*) AS COUNT FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND DEATH_NOTIFICATION_ID <> @DEATH_NOTIFICATION_ID AND (DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'CRTF' OR DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'PROG')
SELECT TOP(1) SDN.* FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION SDN INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON SP.PERSON_ID = SDN.PERSON_ID WHERE SP.MPI_PERSON_ID = @MPI_PERSON_ID ORDER BY DEATH_NOTIFICATION_ID DESC
select top 1 DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE from SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION WITH(NOLOCK) where PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID order by MODIFIED_DATE desc

SELECT SPA.PERSON_ID,SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION SBA INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL SBAD ON SBA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA ON SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID=SPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SBAD.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID WHERE SBAD.JOINT_ANNUITANT_ID = @JOINT_ANNUITANT_ID AND SPBX.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE IN ('JP50','JPOP') AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID =SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.MODIFIED_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL')

select DISTINCT SBA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID AS BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID ,0 AS DRO_APPLICATION_ID from SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION SBA inner join SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL SBAD on SBA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID=SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID=SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID WHERE SBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CNCL') UNION select DISTINCT 0 AS BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID ,SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID AS DRO_APPLICATION_ID from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA inner join SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD on SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID=SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID WHERE SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CNCL')

SELECT DISTINCT SBAD.*,SBA.RETIREMENT_DATE FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION SBA INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL SBAD ON SBA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID WHERE SBA.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RTMT','DSBL') AND SBA.APPLICATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'APPR' AND SBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID

SELECT SPA.* FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID WHERE SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' AND (SELECT TOP(1) STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.MODIFIED_DATE DESC) = 'CMPL'

SELECT SPAS.TERMINATED_STATUS_REASON_VALUE AS istrTerminationReason,SPA.*, SP.FIRST_NAME + '' + SP.LAST_NAME istrPayeeName ,SP1.FIRST_NAME + '' + SP1.LAST_NAME istrParticipantName ,SCV.DESCRIPTION istrPayeeAccountCurrentStatus FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS SPAS ON SPAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON SP.PERSON_ID = SPA.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP1 ON SP1.PERSON_ID = SPBA.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE SCV ON SCV.CODE_ID = spas.STATUS_ID AND SCV.CODE_VALUE = SPAS.STATUS_VALUE WHERE SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and spas.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID = (select top (1) PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID from SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q where q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = spa.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID order by MODIFIED_DATE desc)
select COUNT(*) from SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT where PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID

SELECT DISTINCT SPHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER SPHH INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND PAYMENT_DATE >= @FROM_DATE AND PAYMENT_DATE <= @TODATE

SELECT PA.* FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR PLBXR ON PA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID=PLBXR.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID WHERE (PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE='DDPR' OR PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE='DDPT' OR PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE='RTMT') AND PA.ACCOUNT_RELATION_VALUE='BENE' AND PLBXR.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE in ( '10TC','10LA','2YLA') AND PA.PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID
SELECT DATE_OF_DEATH FROM SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION where PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'PROG'

update SGT_DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_HOUR_INFO set DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_INFO_ID = H.DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_INFO_ID FROM SGT_DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_HOUR_INFO HI INNER JOIN SGT_DATA_EXTRACTION_BATCH_INFO H ON H.PERSON_ID=HI.PERSON_ID WHERE H.YEAR_END_DATA_EXTRACTION_HEADER_ID = @YEAR_END_DATA_EXTRACTION_HEADER_ID
select REPORTED_BY from SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION where PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID and DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE='CRTF'

SELECT * FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WHERE SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RTMT','DSBL') AND (SELECT TOP(1) SPAS.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS SPAS WHERE SPAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC )NOT IN ('CNCL','CMPL')

select p.MPI_PERSON_ID, p.SSN, p.FIRST_NAME, p.LAST_NAME, cast(p.DATE_OF_DEATH as date) DATE_OF_DEATH, cast(dn.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE as date) DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE from dbo.SGT_PERSON p with(nolock) cross apply ( select top 1 with ties cast(dn.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE as date) DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE, dn.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE from dbo.SGT_DEATH_NOTIFICATION dn with(nolock) where 1=1 and dn.PERSON_ID = p.PERSON_ID order by dn.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_ID desc ) dn where 1=1 and p.DATE_OF_DEATH is not null and dn.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_STATUS_VALUE in ('CRTF', 'PROG') and dn.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE between dateadd(yy, -3, cast(getdate() as date)) and cast(getdate() as date) order by dn.DEATH_NOTIFICATION_RECEIVED_DATE
